<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Prac Call Schedule Required</title>
  </head>
  <body
    style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; padding: 20px;"
  >
    <table
      style="max-width:600px; width:100%; margin:auto; border-collapse: collapse;"
    >
      <tr>
        <td style="padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">
          <h2 style="color: #2a7ae2;">Hi {{name}},</h2>
          <p>This call isn’t just a formality—it's how we start protecting your
            assets and move your case forward to a resolution.</p>
          <p>If we don’t speak directly with the IRS today, we can’t pull
            transcripts, pause potential enforcement, or begin working on your
            behalf until your POA is approved. If we wait for paperwork to
            clear, days or even weeks can pass, and that delay can limit your
            options.</p>
          <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-weight: bold;">Call me at
            <a
              href="tel:{{phone}}"
              style="color: #2a7ae2; text-decoration: none;"
            >{{phone}}</a>. Or if needed, use the scheduler in your last email
            to set a time.</p>
          <div style="margin-top: 40px;">
            {{{signature}}}
          </div>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>